Card playing simulation
-----------------------

^cards^
 
Description
-----------

Card playing simulation using buttons to shuffle cards, draw cards 
     without replacement, draw cards with replacement, or play
     blackjack.  After hitting the "Blackjack" button player may
     "Hit" or "Stand."


